dev.nokee.platform.objectivecpp

Interface ObjectiveCppLibrary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseNameAwareComponent, BinaryAwareComponent, Component, DependencyAwareComponent<NativeLibraryComponentDependencies>, HasObjectiveCppSources, HasPrivateHeaders, HasPublicHeaders, ObjectiveCppLibraryExtension, SourceAwareComponent<ObjectiveCppLibrarySources>, TargetBuildTypeAwareComponent, TargetLinkageAwareComponent, TargetMachineAwareComponent, VariantAwareComponent<NativeLibrary>

    public interface ObjectiveCppLibrary
extends ObjectiveCppLibraryExtension, DependencyAwareComponent<NativeLibraryComponentDependencies>, VariantAwareComponent<NativeLibrary>, BinaryAwareComponent, TargetMachineAwareComponent, TargetLinkageAwareComponent, TargetBuildTypeAwareComponent, SourceAwareComponent<ObjectiveCppLibrarySources>, HasPrivateHeaders, HasPublicHeaders, HasObjectiveCppSources, BaseNameAwareComponent
    Configuration for a library written in Objective-C++, defining the dependencies that make up the library plus other settings.

    An instance of this type is added as a project extension by the Objective-C++ Library Plugin.

    Since:
    0.5
